Class ContinuousParameterSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.arbiter.optimize.parameter.continuous.ContinuousParameterSpace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParameterSpace<java.lang.Double>

    public class ContinuousParameterSpace
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParameterSpace<java.lang.Double>
    ContinuousParametSpace is a ParameterSpace<Double> that (optionally) takes an Apache Commons RealDistribution when used for random sampling (such as in a RandomSearchCandidateGenerator)
